title: didnt get the teemo icon for winning doombots
body:
i beat it a couple times the day it came out and i still havnt gotten the icon i even beat it on later dates and didnt get it
IGN iownudie

replies.body: There's a few players that still need to get their icons, and we aim to have it distributed by the 17th per the [Teemoing ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016)page.  Hang tight and the goods will come!
